Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.82,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I’ve no colour
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:41.00,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So the least I can do for you is endure
